com.blukii.infosdk

Interface BlukiiClient.OnResolveServerNewsListener

  • Enclosing class:
    BlukiiClient

    public static interface BlukiiClient.OnResolveServerNewsListener

    Callback interface for retrieving a translated blukii Info Manager news text.



    The callbacks are registered by calling BlukiiClient.resolveServerNews(String, OnResolveServerNewsListener).
    See Also:
    BlukiiClient.resolveServerNews(String, OnResolveServerNewsListener)

      • onNewsResult

        void onNewsResult(java.lang.String news)
        Will be called once after calling BlukiiClient.resolveServerNews(String, OnResolveServerNewsListener).
